Description:
You arrive at the Velkarath Coliseum, here several groups of warriors fight to see who is the best.

You can bet to see which group will win the next fight and double your money or even enter to compete in the arena.

The competition consists of several consecutive matches until you face off against the champion of the arena.
DescriptionAction: Do you want to participate or bet?
